nmap        <M-s>           :write<CR>
vmap        <M-s>           <C-C>:write<CR>
imap        <M-s>           <C-O>:write<CR>

" ALT-Q to close
nmap        <M-q>           :quit<CR>
vmap        <M-q>           <C-C>:quit<CR>
imap        <M-q>           <C-O>:quit<CR>

" comment out lines of code (toggles)
